This paper deals with the optimization of deep neural networks for on-board processing on UAVs, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of semi-supervised online learning tasks, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a new method for model compression, which falls under data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses the optimization of matrix multiplication, which is a topic that falls under numerical analysis (cs.NE).
